sentences: Moeko Matsushita (松下 萌子, Matsushita Moeko) is a Japanese singer and actress from Hyōgo, Japan.
In 2001, Moeko released her first single "Natsu Iro" on the label Avex Trax.
That same year, she released two other singles.
"Sotsugyō" ("Graduation"; a cover of Yuki Saito's 1985 debut single)
